Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CloserPass設置部隊請馬上返回拉莫洛克號空母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:57.40,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(870,650)}Lamorak
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全機 正如你們聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄CloserPass 立即撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則會被拋下的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 Delta中隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體立即離開所搭乘的CloserPass
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同量子次元反應彈一起全數廢棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行庫蓋爾中校的撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去快去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CloserPass量子次元反應彈設置為機雷模式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除安全鎖後開始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群傢伙打算將CloserPass連同能量核一起吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡由我來抵擋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 堅持200秒就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究極限定解除命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒光了也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求援助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓住了 無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求搭救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了 雷德 回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是庫蓋爾中校…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別繼續為此消耗能量了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求援助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求援助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們完全被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人打算捕食CloserPass的量子能源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體已經撐不住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究極限定解除結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認機能安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此後對戰鬥行為加以迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行回路保持連接
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Telemachy躍遷開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉莫洛克號 距Telemachy躍遷開始還有40秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}39 38 37 36…24
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不能就這樣把希迪亞斯也帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你單獨回艦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來拖住那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫蓋爾中校 這是違反軍令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會殺掉比我更多的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我作為軍人的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願人類銀河同盟榮光長存
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接收到導航信標 著艦程序啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的希迪亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝羅茲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特讓我傳話給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果貝羅茲願意負責的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明晚之前可以任意使用這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這是合同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 有夠斤斤計較
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道就不用這麼辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想調查內部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說打開外殼了 連條劃痕都劃不上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本想像不出是怎麼組裝上的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種字我可從來沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 是不是文字都說不准了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:13:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底 這東西被發現的時候就已經很可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既沒生銹也沒腐蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平時打撈上來的寶物完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不開的話就別談什麼寶不寶物了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得按照說好的價格買下 皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管撈上什麼你都要 這可是你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個守財奴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像隨時都會動起來的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正肯定是壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不管敲哪裡都紋絲不動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之也是為了以防萬一才指定這種外沿區域的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是出事 直接捨棄這裡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳 這裡可是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能說捨棄就捨棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 我會跟莉吉特說的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可沒什麼有趣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快繼續你的派送工作去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我早上再來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前可要稍微撬開一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盡量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…有這麼容易就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦波檢測 基礎律動無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認雷德少尉覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復甦成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基於緊急程序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過人工冬眠暫停了貴官的生理機能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過時間為266815分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機系統雖然也已全部凍結
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在外部刺激之下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於12分前重啟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們睡了半年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當前事態需要由駕駛員進行判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此對貴官執行了覺醒進程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知語言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與幾種古代語言相似
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然正在進行解析 但情報不足
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人類銀河同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未加盟的漂流部族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙沒見過Machine Caliber嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測到他們有破壞本機的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎不具備實施手段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測該集團的文明程度極低
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這情況 他們連駕駛艙都打不開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在位置是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法鎖定坐標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定位原點已喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機隨拉莫洛克號空母的Telemachy躍遷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被轉移至計量時空之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在隨機選定的坐標下與通常空間進行了同步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機一面發送求援信號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時維持貴官的人工冬眠狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而事態正不斷朝無法靜觀的方向發展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求探討策略
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看來似乎是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在未知對方身份時無法斷定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測此地隔離壁的構造非常脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以本機目前的功率可將其破壞並逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆外也許是真空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這些傢伙都沒穿增壓服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先確認情況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想調查一下外面的情況 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力正好是1G啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為漂流部族來說 調整得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要成分為氮氣 氧氣 二氧化碳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為生存的理想比例
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外還有其他微量成分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並未檢測出危險物質
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然能呼吸就直接呼吸好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攜帶的氧氣還是盡量節約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這地方怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落後也要有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說過讓你早上來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是天根本還沒亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意嘛 所以就醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一點沒睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為除了皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人能打開這裡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可是橫渡銀河期間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨意浪費電的話又要被莉吉特…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 這東西可不會動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 快離開那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 放手 放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴官的行動毫無邏輯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓個人質的話 對方起碼不會攻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…但願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先把握這裡的構造
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前不能讓你發動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解 開始記錄影像進行解析
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡可能大範圍移動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道這些傢伙在說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解析進行率40%左右
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要更多的詞彙樣本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 所以你多說點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是火災？怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特 有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他帶著奇妙的武器 艾米被他擄走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說入侵者？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就出現在機庫裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的發言中提及「與母親進行生殖」及「神聖的排泄物」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是些正經人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說漂流部族…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:20:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表示懷疑 無法斷定該集團為漂流部族
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據至今所收集到的所有影像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全未檢測出與重力變化 輻射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及氣密性相關的設備和措施
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測該設施的設計環境與真空及失重完全無緣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太扯了 這不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 記錄中存在著唯一的特例
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這裡到底是哪裡
